  <li><strong>Itchy skin, recurrent ear trouble or a chicken sensitivity?</strong> Grain-free, single-protein, gently-cooked recipes are gentlest — Forthglade, Years and Butternut all qualify (check the protein source if chicken is a trigger).</li>
